  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<ol>\n  <li>Experience would be a plus in project planning, control and site management of various construction project, we welcome fresh graduates too.</li>\n  <li>Attend site meeting, inspection and monitoring of project progress</li>\n  <li>Ability to interact and liaise with consultants &amp; subcontractors at all levels</li>\n  <li>Self motivated and can work independently</li>\n  <li>Involved in the quality control and assurance</li>\n  <li>Ad hoc assignments</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Civil/Structural Engineering</li>\n  <li>Good written communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to use AutoCAD</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently, multi-task hardworking</li>\n  <li>Preferably able to commence within short notice</li>\n</ul>",
